Class Warehouse

java.lang.Object
  Vertex
      Warehouse

public class Warehouse
extends Vertex

This class defines the setup for the warehouse. The warehouses essentially just dispatches the trucks and keeps track of which trucks come from which warehouse. It has a few instance variables--it keeps track of the number of trucks, has an array of trucks, and a count of the next truck that will leave the warehouse.
